overview.title: Annual General Meeting
overview.excerpt: Join us for the Annual General Meeting to review the year, hear reports, and re-elect all club positions.

details.title: Annual General Meeting
details.longDescription: The Annual General Meeting (AGM) is a key event where we review the club's activities throughout the year, hear the President's and Treasurer's reports, and re-elect all club positions. All members are encouraged to attend and have their say in shaping the future of the club.
